The 200 response is the primary outcome for this endpoint, representing the successful rendering of the post comments page as HTML. No explicit error responses are defined in the provided code path, and route-model binding will automatically trigger a 404 if the post is not found, but that behavior is outside the explicit 200 response object for this method.

